# Task #120: the fetch hook renders REAL download progress via show2.elf. Deterministic
# assertions: the daemon comes up with the marker-free game name (task #126 display rule),
# and 100% is painted ONLY after the honest success check (rc=0 AND real bytes on card).
desc fetch hook (#120): download progress renders via show2 — daemon up, 100% only after verified bytes
invoke prehook
config paired
romarg Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✘ Zelda.gba
sdfile Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✘ Zelda.gba
engine 0|RESULT downloaded=1
expect_exit 0
expect_trace ENGINE --download
expect_trace SHOW2 daemon text='Downloading Zelda…'
expect_trace SHOW2 TEXT:Downloaded ✓
expect_trace SHOW2 PROGRESS:100
expect_file_has Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✘ Zelda.gba	DLBYTES
